on takeoff. ; Photo, Alaska crash survivors from left, front row, are: Roman 
Tcheremenylch, 11-year-old Tony Aliengena and his family, Gary, Alaina and 
Susan. Standing, from left, are: Jim Carlton, Joseph Lee, Susan Eisner and 
Gunter Hagen. Associated Press; Map, Crash site, Los Angeles Times 
</P>
