ALIENGENA, TONY; AIRPLANE ACCIDENTS -- ALASKA; FEATS; AIRPLANE SAFETY; 
AIRPLANES -- OVERCROWDING; HEALTH AND SAFETY VIOLATIONS; ALIENGENA, GARY; 
CIRCUMNAVIGATION; PILOTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
